Analyze current active hosts and compare to previous state
Log state changes

Script list arp table.
Load last state.
Handle exceptions.
Check if hosts realy active (ping)
Compare states and log state changes is such way:

2014-09-12 00:40:02,744 - net_activity - INFO - Host host1.domain.local become inactive
2014-09-12 00:50:02,310 - net_activity - INFO - Host host1.domain.local become active

Script must be executed in such way:

/python-path /script-path